    "long_instructions": "## Format\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you become a professional food critic. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n\r\n>You are a professional food critic. Generate some ideas for how to evaluate a new restaurant.\r\n\r\n2. Here are some **format** ideas you can add to your prompt:\r\n    - Bullet points\r\n    - A five-paragraph essay\r\n    - A numbered list\r\n3. Revise your prompt to AI Chat by adding in **Format**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n4. Find and complete the section in your Unit Guide called \"Format\". \r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what format to add?**]\r\nTry copy and pasting the following revised prompt into AI Chat: \r\n>You are a professional food critic. Generate a numbered list in order of importance, from most to least important, of what to consider when evaluating a new restaurant.\r\n:::",
